{{Quote|There was a large Caamasi refugee group on Alderaan when I was growing up, living in the South Islands in secret under my father's protection. They were hoping that someday when they were strong enough they could return to Camaas and try to rebuild.|[[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] to [[Talon Karrde]]|<ref name="Specter of the Past">''[[Specter of the Past]]''</ref>}}
The '''South Islands''' were located on [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]], and contained a large and secret [[Caamasi/Legends|Caamasi]] refugee population who died with the [[Destruction of Alderaan/Legends|Destruction of Alderaan]] in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]].

